  "text": "Motorola MA1 $35 $70 Save $35 Power Source USB What's Included N/A Brand Motorola Sound Connectivity Wi-Fi, Bluetooth Dimensions 3.06 x 1.22 x 0.12\" (with cable) The Motorola MA1 adds wireless Android Auto to your car in just a few seconds with as little fuss as possible. Designed in collaboration with Google, it works surprisingly well on a wide range of vehicles but lacks advanced configuration options.  It took some time, but Android Auto is now available in a lot of cars by default. Of course, the experience will be different depending on what vehicle you have, but at the very least, you're going to need to plug in your phone in order to get it working. If you're someone in that situation, it isn't all that bad, but it could definitely be better, which is where the Motorola MA1 wireless adapter comes in. Related With the Motorola MA1, you're going to get a smooth and seamless experience that really brings Android Auto to another level. You'll no longer have to plug in your phone, with things just connecting to your head unit as soon as you turn on your car. The best part is that it doesn't cost all that much, thanks to this deep discount that drops the MA1 down to just $35. What's great about the Motorola MA1 wireless Android Auto adapter? As far as what you get, it's a pretty simple device, with a USB-A port on one side that's meant to plug into your vehicle's USB port. From there, it's just about pairing the device to your phone, and seeing Android Auto come alive without any cables attached to your phone. The MA1 is sleek and compact, making it easy to store, no matter the vehicle. Plus, you get impressive connectivity here thanks to the device's Google Bridge technology and 5Ghz Wi-Fi signal. And just in case you have two devices, the MA1 one can handle that with ease. This is one of those devices that makes a world of difference and doesn't cost a whole lot, delivering fantastic bang for your buck. So be sure to grab it while you can for this special price because at 50% off, it won't be around for long.",
