/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                \n                        \n            \n            \n                                        \n                                        \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                    \n                    \u003cimg width=\"5551\" height=\"3701\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"ma1 hero-1\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/ma1-hero-1.jpg\"/\u003e\n        \n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWith the Motorola MA1, you\u0026#39;re going to get a smooth and seamless experience that really brings Android Auto to another level. You\u0026#39;ll no longer have to plug in your phone, with things just connecting to your head unit as soon as you turn on your car. The best part is that it doesn\u0026#39;t cost all that much, thanks to this deep discount that drops the MA1 down to just $35. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"what-39-s-great-about-the-motorola-ma1-wireless-android-auto-adapter\"\u003e\n                        What\u0026#39;s great about the Motorola MA1 wireless Android Auto adapter?\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                \n    \n\u003cp\u003eAs far as what you get, it\u0026#39;s a pretty simple device, with a USB-A port on one side that\u0026#39;s meant to plug into your vehicle\u0026#39;s USB port. From there, it\u0026#39;s just about pairing the device to your phone, and seeing Android Auto come alive without any cables attached to your phone. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eThe MA1 is sleek and compact, making it easy to store, no matter the vehicle. Plus, you get impressive connectivity here thanks to the device\u0026#39;s Google Bridge technology and 5Ghz Wi-Fi signal. And just in case you have two devices, the MA1 one can handle that with ease.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eThis is one of those devices that makes a world of difference and doesn\u0026#39;t cost a whole lot, delivering fantastic bang for your buck. So be sure to grab it while you can for this special price because at 50% off, it won\u0026#39;t be around for long. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
